@startuml
autonumber

actor "Backoffice Operator" as Admin
participant "AirportController" as Ctrl
participant "AirportRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Dados" as DB

Admin -> Ctrl : GET /api/airports/statistics/busiest?limit={N}
activate Ctrl

note right of Ctrl: CQRS: Como é uma consulta estatística,\no Controller interroga o Repository diretamente.
Ctrl -> Repo : findBusiestAirports(limit)
activate Repo

note right of Repo: Executa uma query de agregação\n(ex: SELECT iata, COUNT(routes) \nGROUP BY iata ORDER BY count DESC)
Repo -> DB : SELECT ... GROUP BY ... ORDER BY ... LIMIT ?
activate DB
DB --> Repo : List<BusiestAirportDto>
deactivate DB

Repo --> Ctrl : List<BusiestAirportDto>
deactivate Repo

Ctrl --> Admin : 200 OK (Estatísticas dos Aeroportos)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml